I told you.

278
00:19:46,475 --> 00:19:50,174
I don't think our kiss was a mistake.

279
00:19:50,174 --> 00:19:53,794
I'm not going to pretend it never happened, so...

280
00:19:54,593 --> 00:19:56,873
- unless you don't like me and avoid me─ - Director,

281
00:19:56,873 --> 00:19:59,213
I think you forgot. We're at work.

282
00:19:59,213 --> 00:20:01,232
You are the director.

283
00:20:01,232 --> 00:20:05,312
Not just any director, but Yongsung's heir.

284
00:20:07,681 --> 00:20:10,851
And I am your subordinate.

285
00:20:12,221 --> 00:20:14,620
You don't want to let it rest?

286
00:20:14,620 --> 00:20:16,530
What do you want to do then?

287
00:20:16,530 --> 00:20:18,990
Will you hold my hand?

288
00:20:18,990 --> 00:20:21,689
Can you hold my hand and go outside?

289
00:20:21,689 --> 00:20:24,039
Can you imagine yourself like this...

290
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:26,719
Stand in front of people and the chairperson?

291
00:20:30,498 --> 00:20:32,768
I don't want that either.

292
00:20:34,038 --> 00:20:36,297
I am not interested in being fired.

293
00:20:36,297 --> 00:20:38,197
Also...

294
00:20:43,516 --> 00:20:45,166
We have nothing to discuss.

295
00:20:45,166 --> 00:20:46,846
We don't have to.

296
00:20:47,896 --> 00:20:49,395
I...

297
00:20:59,804 --> 00:21:03,953
♫ ♫

298
00:21:03,953 --> 00:21:09,162
♫ ♫

299
00:21:09,162 --> 00:21:12,702
I think you understand what I mean.

300
00:21:12,702 --> 00:21:15,481
♫ ♫

301
00:21:15,481 --> 00:21:19,221
♫ ♫

302
00:21:19,221 --> 00:21:24,100
♫ ♫

303
00:21:24,100 --> 00:21:27,950
♫ ♫

304
00:21:27,950 --> 00:21:32,969
♫ ♫

305
00:21:40,328 --> 00:21:43,797
Have you forgotten that I confessed my feelings to you?

306
00:21:43,797 --> 00:21:45,277
Oh, that?

307
00:21:45,277 --> 00:21:47,777
Have you forgotten that I said "no"??

308
00:21:47,777 --> 00:21:52,046
If that's why you came here, I find that somewhat unpleasant.

309
00:21:59,855 --> 00:22:02,004
I thought you had gone home.

310
00:22:02,004 --> 00:22:04,724
I was just lost in thought.

311
00:22:04,724 --> 00:22:06,884
Come in. Come in.

312
00:22:09,633 --> 00:22:11,403
Yes.

313
00:22:11,403 --> 00:22:14,773
What? She's getting married?

314
00:22:14,773 --> 00:22:16,272
Our classmate?

315
00:22:16,272 --> 00:22:19,622
Yes, it seems like only yesterday that she was chasing after you in 12th grade.

316
00:22:19,622 --> 00:22:22,461
She probably wasn't the only one.

317
00:22:22,461 --> 00:22:24,401
She wants to hand us the invitation in person.

318
00:22:24,401 --> 00:22:25,881
Okay.

319
00:22:25,881 --> 00:22:27,831
Have you finished work yet?

320
00:22:27,831 --> 00:22:29,630
Should we go for a drink if you have time?

321
00:22:29,630 --> 00:22:31,220
Agreed. Sounds good.

322
00:22:31,220 --> 00:22:33,590
Shall we meet again at Sulo?

323
00:22:38,649 --> 00:22:39,729
Let's go somewhere else.

324
00:22:39,729 --> 00:22:41,349
I'm not going there anymore.

325
00:22:41,349 --> 00:22:43,738
Why? The food was good.

326
00:22:45,348 --> 00:22:47,498
Because I don't want her to feel uncomfortable in my presence.

327
00:22:47,498 --> 00:22:48,958
What did you say?

328
00:22:48,958 --> 00:22:50,037
Was?

329
00:22:50,037 --> 00:22:53,897
I think I've been there too often.

330
00:22:53,897 --> 00:22:57,116
I will never go there again.

331
00:23:02,366 --> 00:23:05,205
[Grace]

332
00:23:06,745 --> 00:23:08,895
What am I doing here?

333
00:23:08,895 --> 00:23:11,724
I thought I was on my way home.

334
00:23:20,873 --> 00:23:23,432
♫ Everything has already been said and done ♫

335
00:23:23,432 --> 00:23:24,562
You're welcome.

336
00:23:24,562 --> 00:23:26,882
♫ And everything you hear, ♫

337
00:23:26,882 --> 00:23:30,801
♫ is only the echo within a shadow ♫

338
00:23:31,871 --> 00:23:38,470
♫ I know there's nothing I can say that you haven't already heard ♫

339
00:23:38,470 --> 00:23:42,620
♫ Although I can tell you for sure ♫

340
00:23:42,620 --> 00:23:46,999
[Grace]

341
00:23:49,608 --> 00:23:54,088
♫ Darling, don't worry ♫

342
00:23:56,517 --> 00:24:01,827
♫ Don't be afraid of the darkness ♫

343
00:24:01,827 --> 00:24:07,406
♫ The blankets will keep you warm ♫

344
00:24:07,406 --> 00:24:13,095
♫ We can weather the storm ♫

345
00:24:27,273 --> 00:24:30,702
It is said that distance makes affection grow.

346
00:24:37,431 --> 00:24:39,911
You were mentioned several times at the last supervisory board meeting.

347
00:24:39,911 --> 00:24:41,801
and everyone reacted positively.

348
00:24:41,801 --> 00:24:44,690
They also seemed enthusiastic about the renovation project.

349
00:24:44,690 --> 00:24:46,490
Good to hear.

350
00:24:47,980 --> 00:24:50,569
Since they were officially introduced,

351
00:24:50,569 --> 00:24:54,609
People seem to be treating you differently now.

352
00:24:54,609 --> 00:24:56,669
Because I have a greater responsibility,

353
00:24:56,669 --> 00:24:59,078
I should work harder.

354
00:25:08,717 --> 00:25:11,096
You are the director.

355
00:25:11,096 --> 00:25:15,176
Not just any director, but Yongsung's legacy.

356
00:25:17,715 --> 00:25:19,855
And I am your employee.

357
00:25:19,855 --> 00:25:21,985
Also...

358
00:25:22,765 --> 00:25:24,484
There's nothing to discuss.

359
00:25:24,484 --> 00:25:26,274
We don't need that.

360
00:25:31,123 --> 00:25:34,203
She even looked beautiful at that moment.

361
00:25:35,133 --> 00:25:36,923
Baek Su Jeong.

362
00:25:47,981 --> 00:25:49,141
I saw the article.

363
00:25:49,141 --> 00:25:52,010
That was a good photo. When did you take it?

364
00:25:52,630 --> 00:25:55,630
Do you have anything carbonated? Or coffee?

365
00:25:55,630 --> 00:25:58,199
I don't have any. Drink this.

366
00:26:00,979 --> 00:26:02,749
Correct.

367
00:26:03,619 --> 00:26:06,898
I should drink cold water and wake up.

368
00:26:06,898 --> 00:26:09,488
What's suddenly going on?

369
00:26:09,488 --> 00:26:11,957
I just wanted to congratulate you.

370
00:26:11,957 --> 00:26:15,787
By the way, do I need a reason to visit you?

371
00:26:15,787 --> 00:26:17,776
Don't you think so?

372
00:26:21,836 --> 00:26:24,006
To be honest,

373
00:26:24,995 --> 00:26:28,045
I had the feeling that I needed to go somewhere.

374
00:26:29,145 --> 00:26:31,854
Otherwise, I would have gone back there.

375
00:26:32,824 --> 00:26:34,604
Ju Yeon,

376
00:26:34,604 --> 00:26:36,754
Do you know why General Kim Yu Sin

377
00:26:36,754 --> 00:26:38,353
has beheaded his horse?

378
00:26:38,353 --> 00:26:43,023
Do you mean General Kim Yu Sin, who was born in the year 595?

379
00:26:43,023 --> 00:26:44,752
He is an admirable general,

380
00:26:44,752 --> 00:26:49,042
But he blamed his horse for his weak willpower.

381
00:26:49,042 --> 00:26:51,731
- Why? - Hm?

382
00:26:51,731 --> 00:26:53,191
Yes.

383
00:26:53,191 --> 00:26:56,211
Yes you are right.

384
00:26:57,351 --> 00:27:00,330
But I can understand how he felt.

385
00:27:02,170 --> 00:27:06,579
I can't tie myself up.

386
00:27:07,229 --> 00:27:10,199
My head tells me I shouldn't...

387
00:27:11,488 --> 00:27:13,678
But I miss her.

388
00:27:15,108 --> 00:27:16,908
Is that the reason?

389
00:27:18,677 --> 00:27:23,117
My body always goes to her.

390
00:27:25,676 --> 00:27:29,616
Goodness, I need to pull myself together.

391
00:27:32,795 --> 00:27:34,845
One always acts with the heart,

392
00:27:35,745 --> 00:27:38,184
before you do it with your head.

393
00:27:39,864 --> 00:27:42,994
Is this what it means to like someone...?

394
00:27:43,974 --> 00:27:46,673
That I really can't give up?

395
00:27:56,742 --> 00:27:59,371
[Yongsung Kaufhaus]

396
00:28:09,080 --> 00:28:11,050
Good morning

397
00:28:12,309 --> 00:28:14,879
Ah yes.

398
00:28:26,217 --> 00:28:29,527
Yes, we agreed to meet again tomorrow for lunch.

399
00:28:29,527 --> 00:28:31,617
I will send out invitations.

400
00:28:32,396 --> 00:28:34,496
Do you know Baekyonggak?

401
00:28:34,496 --> 00:28:36,946
I've heard it's difficult to make a reservation there.

402
00:28:38,505 --> 00:28:39,825
I know.

403
00:28:39,825 --> 00:28:42,215
I admire the effort.

404
00:28:42,215 --> 00:28:44,755
But I will pay for the food.

405
00:28:45,534 --> 00:28:47,064
Oh...

406
00:28:47,064 --> 00:28:49,154
In order.

407
00:28:53,783 --> 00:28:55,823
Who are you meeting up with?

408
00:28:58,633 --> 00:29:01,812
Is this the man I saw you with in the department store?

409
00:29:04,012 --> 00:29:05,801
That's personal.

410
00:29:05,801 --> 00:29:09,331
I don't think I need to answer that, Director.

411
00:29:55,334 --> 00:29:57,694
Yes, we agreed to meet again tomorrow for lunch.

412
00:29:57,694 --> 00:29:59,823
Do you know Baekyonggak?

413
00:29:59,823 --> 00:30:02,283
I've heard it's difficult to make a reservation there.

414
00:30:14,111 --> 00:30:15,741
I thought I should do that.

415
00:30:15,741 --> 00:30:17,221
- Is he crazy? - It could be a surprise.

416
00:30:17,221 --> 00:30:18,581
Man, what should I do?

417
00:30:18,581 --> 00:30:20,650
Who is this man?

418
00:30:22,470 --> 00:30:24,040
Stop!

419
00:30:24,040 --> 00:30:25,820
That's enough now.

420
00:30:27,739 --> 00:30:29,549
Director.

421
00:30:29,549 --> 00:30:31,649
What are you doing here?

422
00:30:32,579 --> 00:30:34,288
Father?

423
00:30:35,908 --> 00:30:37,758
Su Bin's girlfriend?

424
00:30:37,758 --> 00:30:39,338
Didn't you say you'd met her before?

425
00:30:39,338 --> 00:30:42,607
Yes, we've agreed to meet for lunch tomorrow.

426
00:30:42,607 --> 00:30:43,807
It is a pleasure for me.

427
00:30:43,807 --> 00:30:45,547
Lunch? Where?

428
00:30:45,547 --> 00:30:47,456
Do you know Baekyonggak?

429
00:30:47,456 --> 00:30:48,896
I heard there's a reservation there.

430
00:30:48,896 --> 00:30:50,776
This is a famous restaurant.

431
00:30:50,776 --> 00:30:51,966
But they aren't even married yet.

432
00:30:51,966 --> 00:30:53,455
Why should she spoil you?

433
00:30:53,455 --> 00:30:54,725
I know.

434
00:30:54,725 --> 00:30:56,625
I appreciate the effort.

435
00:30:56,625 --> 00:30:58,885
But I will pay for the food.

436
00:30:59,904 --> 00:31:02,354
They were the ones who paid Dad's hospital bill.

437
00:31:02,354 --> 00:31:05,134
This director?

438
00:31:05,134 --> 00:31:08,703
Hello, I am Baek Su Bin, the eldest son.

439
00:31:08,703 --> 00:31:12,193
What brings you here, Mr. Director?

440
00:31:13,402 --> 00:31:15,762
I'll meet someone here too.

441
00:31:15,762 --> 00:31:17,702
I met you here by chance.

442
00:31:17,702 --> 00:31:19,122
I understand.

443
00:31:19,122 --> 00:31:20,301
Then we will let you go now.

444
00:31:20,301 --> 00:31:23,181
But they just cancelled on me.

445
00:31:23,181 --> 00:31:25,841
Do you mind if I join you?

446
00:31:27,250 --> 00:31:29,090
Well, we're having a family dinner.

447
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:30,680
Yongsun is a family.

448
00:31:30,680 --> 00:31:31,920
Wouldn't that be okay?

449
00:31:31,920 --> 00:31:35,029
Team leader Baek has recently achieved something great.

450
00:31:35,029 --> 00:31:37,509
I was planning to invite her to dinner anyway.

451
00:31:37,509 --> 00:31:39,589
Was that our Su Jeong?

452
00:31:39,589 --> 00:31:41,388
Su Bing's girlfriend is coming.

453
00:31:41,388 --> 00:31:43,388
Oh my goodness. It's alright. It's fine.

454
00:31:43,388 --> 00:31:44,798
She is a social butterfly.

455
00:31:44,798 --> 00:31:46,418
She is not shy.

456
00:31:46,967 --> 00:31:48,257
Why don't we sit down?

457
00:31:48,257 --> 00:31:51,177
I will tell you what she did, where and when,

458
00:31:51,177 --> 00:31:52,957
down to the smallest detail.

459
00:31:52,957 --> 00:31:56,266
Sounds good. Please sit down. Yes.

460
00:32:01,445 --> 00:32:03,415
Thanks to team leader Baek,

461
00:32:03,415 --> 00:32:05,465
We were able to convince CEO An.

462
00:32:05,465 --> 00:32:07,374
Because she is so persistent.

463
00:32:07,374 --> 00:32:09,264
I don't know where she got that from.

464
00:32:09,264 --> 00:32:12,594
She must have gotten it from her wonderful father.

465
00:32:12,594 --> 00:32:16,303
They really have a good eye for people.

466
00:32:16,863 --> 00:32:19,303
I have a tendency towards that.

467
00:32:19,303 --> 00:32:20,782
I knew it.

468
00:32:20,782 --> 00:32:22,362
What do we do now?

469
00:32:22,362 --> 00:32:24,812
Ye Na unfortunately cannot come due to an emergency call.

470
00:32:24,812 --> 00:32:27,101
Really? Then we can't change it.

471
00:32:27,101 --> 00:32:30,191
His girlfriend is a police officer.

472
00:32:30,191 --> 00:32:31,521
She feels terrible.

473
00:32:31,521 --> 00:32:33,930
She congratulates you again on having your plaster cast removed.

474
00:32:33,930 --> 00:32:35,410
She wants to invite us next time.

475
00:32:35,410 --> 00:32:38,390
Tell her that I appreciate the gesture alone.

476
00:32:38,390 --> 00:32:41,519
Then I can invite you to this meal today.

477
00:32:41,519 --> 00:32:43,509
Help yourself to plenty.

478
00:32:43,509 --> 00:32:44,889
Who said that you─

479
00:32:44,889 --> 00:32:46,439
Excuse me!

480
00:32:47,139 --> 00:32:50,008
Please bring us the menu.

481
00:32:53,928 --> 00:32:55,717
Thank you so much for the food.

482
00:32:59,417 --> 00:33:01,656
Excuse me, Mr. Ban.

483
00:33:05,126 --> 00:33:07,266
I wasn't sure, but

484
00:33:07,266 --> 00:33:10,235
You're interested in my sister? Is that correct?

485
00:33:10,865 --> 00:33:12,735
My dad told me,

486
00:33:12,735 --> 00:33:14,364
that you are Yongsun's company heir.

487
00:33:14,364 --> 00:33:19,274
You are an impressive person. Why my sister?

488
00:33:19,274 --> 00:33:22,223
I don't know what you think about her,

489
00:33:22,223 --> 00:33:24,583
But she is very valuable to us.

490
00:33:24,583 --> 00:33:27,443
She has been through a lot and sacrificed a lot.

491
00:33:27,443 --> 00:33:28,862
When people looked down on me,

492
00:33:28,862 --> 00:33:31,662
She played a video game for me instead.

493
00:33:31,662 --> 00:33:34,861
So if you do this carelessly, just to mess around,

494
00:33:34,861 --> 00:33:37,541
I will not let you get away with this.

495
00:33:41,790 --> 00:33:44,420
You don't need to worry about that.

496
00:33:47,220 --> 00:33:50,919
I don't do this lightly.

497
00:33:55,398 --> 00:33:59,218
Madam Chairwoman, what you asked me to do has been done.

498
00:33:59,218 --> 00:34:01,118
- Already? - Yes.

499
00:34:01,118 --> 00:34:04,877
They are really fast and thorough.

500
00:34:04,877 --> 00:34:06,347
For this reason

501
00:34:06,347 --> 00:34:08,826
I also asked you to clean Director Ban's apartment.

502
00:34:08,826 --> 00:34:11,456
They do a good job there too, don't they?

503
00:34:12,136 --> 00:34:15,355
Everything is fine, but he said I shouldn't enter his study.

504
00:34:15,355 --> 00:34:17,225
He said it doesn't need to be cleaned.

505
00:34:17,225 --> 00:34:18,915
The study?

506
00:34:18,915 --> 00:34:20,765
What does he keep in it?

507
00:34:20,765 --> 00:34:22,374
I'm not sure,

508
00:34:22,374 --> 00:34:25,594
But it looked like there was video surveillance there.

509
00:34:28,333 --> 00:34:30,693
Okay. You can leave now.

510
00:34:35,512 --> 00:34:38,222
[Chief Kwon In Gyeong]

511
00:34:44,461 --> 00:34:47,091
You wanted to see me, Madam Chairwoman.

512
00:34:47,091 --> 00:34:49,460
You can go in now.

513
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,949
Once we're finished here,

514
00:34:54,949 --> 00:34:57,699
We're going to Director Ban's apartment.

515
00:34:57,699 --> 00:34:59,079
What's this all about so suddenly?

516
00:34:59,079 --> 00:35:01,708
I need to check his study.

517
00:35:01,708 --> 00:35:04,528
He doesn't let anyone in there.

518
00:35:04,528 --> 00:35:09,227
I'm curious what important stuff he has there.

519
00:35:09,227 --> 00:35:10,917
I will inform Director Ban.

520
00:35:10,917 --> 00:35:12,397
No.

521
00:35:12,397 --> 00:35:14,347
That's not necessary.

522
00:35:25,415 --> 00:35:28,495
Where are your father and your brother?

523
00:35:30,044 --> 00:35:33,004
I let her go because I have something to say.

524
00:35:34,304 --> 00:35:36,663
What exactly do you think?

525
00:35:36,663 --> 00:35:39,523
Why did you come here?

526
00:35:39,523 --> 00:35:41,633
I thought we had finished the subject last time.

527
00:35:41,633 --> 00:35:43,662
I thought you understood.

528
00:35:45,932 --> 00:35:48,102
It was because I was afraid.

529
00:35:52,031 --> 00:35:54,571
While I behave so foolishly,

530
00:35:54,571 --> 00:35:57,620
and you would like another one

531
00:35:59,210 --> 00:36:00,560
What should I do then?

532
00:36:00,560 --> 00:36:02,639
I don't like that.

533
00:36:04,669 --> 00:36:06,949
Understanding does not mean that...

534
00:36:08,329 --> 00:36:10,938
I have no feelings anymore.

535
00:36:27,406 --> 00:36:28,366
Yes, Chief.

536
00:36:28,366 --> 00:36:30,435
Once the event ends,

537
00:36:30,435 --> 00:36:32,295
The chairwoman wants to visit your apartment.

538
00:36:32,295 --> 00:36:34,115
She's coming to my house?

539
00:36:34,115 --> 00:36:37,464
Yes. We'll leave in two hours.

540
00:36:37,464 --> 00:36:39,474
She seems to think

541
00:36:39,474 --> 00:36:43,033
that there is something in your study.

542
00:36:50,512 --> 00:36:52,882
I have to go home immediately.

543
00:36:52,882 --> 00:36:54,082
What's up?

544
00:36:54,082 --> 00:36:55,582
What's wrong with her coming to your house?

545
00:36:55,582 --> 00:36:56,901
The study.

546
00:36:56,901 --> 00:36:59,171
She will find out that it...

547
00:37:00,391 --> 00:37:02,830
Calm down for a moment.

548
00:37:03,730 --> 00:37:05,350
Ahjummoni, please. Ahjummoni...

549
00:37:05,350 --> 00:37:07,240
Forgive me just once, Ahjummoni.

550
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:08,930
Don't do that, Ahjummoni.

551
00:37:08,930 --> 00:37:11,779
Oh my! Oh my!

552
00:37:13,549 --> 00:37:16,518
Everything could burn and disappear.

553
00:37:17,888 --> 00:37:20,058
The things I value.

554
00:37:22,138 --> 00:37:24,487
- Step aside. - And what if you proceed that way?

555
00:37:24,487 --> 00:37:26,627
Do you have a plan?

556
00:37:30,396 --> 00:37:33,036
Let's buy some time first.

557
00:37:35,746 --> 00:37:39,095
[2024 Future Energy Industry Expo]

558
00:37:39,955 --> 00:37:41,865
Madam Chairwoman.

559
00:37:42,765 --> 00:37:44,074
Good day.

560
00:37:44,074 --> 00:37:45,954
You remember me, don't you? I'm Shin Won.

561
00:37:45,954 --> 00:37:47,184
Kim Shin Won.

562
00:37:47,184 --> 00:37:48,914
Yes.

563
00:37:48,914 --> 00:37:50,783
Long time no see.

564
00:37:50,783 --> 00:37:54,493
I've heard that you're still friends with Director Ban.

565
00:37:54,493 --> 00:37:55,953
Yes, of course.

566
00:37:55,953 --> 00:37:57,812
We are basically like brothers.

567
00:37:57,812 --> 00:38:00,032
Since he started working at the department store,

568
00:38:00,032 --> 00:38:02,122
We can spend more time together.

569
00:38:02,122 --> 00:38:03,561
Is that so?

570
00:38:03,561 --> 00:38:07,971
Incidentally, you haven't changed at all.

571
00:38:07,971 --> 00:38:10,130
Does time pass you by without leaving a trace?

572
00:38:10,130 --> 00:38:13,100
The PR team at headquarters should try harder.

573
00:38:13,100 --> 00:38:15,130
Your photos don't do it justice.

574
00:38:15,130 --> 00:38:17,819
They look so young and beautiful.

575
00:38:19,409 --> 00:38:22,549
They're still good at chatting.

576
00:38:22,549 --> 00:38:23,888
Thank you.

577
00:38:23,888 --> 00:38:26,968
By the way, what brings you here?

578
00:38:26,968 --> 00:38:30,137
Oh, yes, I was just in the area.

579
00:38:30,137 --> 00:38:32,087
Have you eaten yet, Madam Chairwoman?

580
00:38:32,087 --> 00:38:34,667
If not, would you like to join me?

581
00:38:34,667 --> 00:38:36,147
When would I ever again

582
00:38:36,147 --> 00:38:39,296
have the honor of going out to dinner with you?

583
00:38:39,296 --> 00:38:40,736
Yes.

584
00:38:40,736 --> 00:38:42,466
I'm sorry,

585
00:38:42,466 --> 00:38:44,595
But I have to go. I'm busy.

586
00:38:44,595 --> 00:38:46,335
Madam Chairwoman.

587
00:38:46,335 --> 00:38:49,645
How about a cup of tea?

588
00:38:49,645 --> 00:38:52,884
Stop taking up any more of my time.

589
00:38:54,664 --> 00:38:56,684
P-Take care of yourself.

590
00:39:00,893 --> 00:39:02,463
[Bbanjju]

591
00:39:03,902 --> 00:39:06,632
Yes, I tried to stop her,

592
00:39:06,632 --> 00:39:08,352
But going out to eat with her is going too far.

593
00:39:08,352 --> 00:39:10,611
What exactly is going on?

594
00:39:10,611 --> 00:39:12,161
If you park your truck here,

595
00:39:12,161 --> 00:39:14,371
What about the other cars?

596
00:39:14,371 --> 00:39:16,251
Toilet?

597
00:39:17,650 --> 00:39:20,230
I will call the police if you do not come immediately.

598
00:39:20,230 --> 00:39:22,120
A lot of time has passed.

599
00:39:22,120 --> 00:39:25,519
Should I postpone the visit to the director's house?

600
00:39:25,519 --> 00:39:27,009
That's fine.

601
00:39:27,539 --> 00:39:29,479
It would only take a moment anyway.

602
00:39:29,479 --> 00:39:30,998
They have another appointment after that.

603
00:39:30,998 --> 00:39:33,298
Why are we still talking?

604
00:39:34,088 --> 00:39:36,108
I'm sorry.

605
00:39:40,697 --> 00:39:43,557
I'm sorry, I was in such a hurry.

606
00:39:43,557 --> 00:39:47,226
I think a car could easily fit through here.

607
00:39:47,226 --> 00:39:48,596
How strange.

608
00:39:48,596 --> 00:39:51,845
What does "parked in the middle of the street" mean?

609
00:39:51,845 --> 00:39:53,365
Did I do that?

610
00:39:53,365 --> 00:39:55,725
But I guess you can't...

611
00:39:55,725 --> 00:39:57,674
You can't just drive off like that.

612
00:39:57,674 --> 00:40:00,004
Anyway. Drive your truck away now.

613
00:40:00,004 --> 00:40:01,314
Okay, okay.

614
00:40:01,314 --> 00:40:03,764
I feel really bad, by the way.

615
00:40:03,764 --> 00:40:05,953
Shall I cut you some sashimi?

616
00:40:06,623 --> 00:40:09,043
I have a load of fish, directly from Jeju─

617
00:40:09,043 --> 00:40:12,862
Get your truck out of the way and stop this nonsense!

618
00:40:13,892 --> 00:40:15,482
I guess you don't want to.

619
00:40:15,482 --> 00:40:17,841
All right! Okay.

620
00:40:34,329 --> 00:40:35,759
I, Su Jeong.

621
00:40:35,759 --> 00:40:38,278
I did my best, but...

622
00:40:38,278 --> 00:40:41,328
So why are you trying to stop the chairwoman?

623
00:41:07,014 --> 00:41:09,724
Will you tell me later?

624
00:41:10,624 --> 00:41:12,583
Huh? Okay.

625
00:41:12,583 --> 00:41:15,173
Hello Hello...

626
00:41:15,923 --> 00:41:17,563
Was?

627
00:41:20,702 --> 00:41:23,112
I can't believe I ran into you here by chance.

628
00:41:24,861 --> 00:41:27,471
I know. What brings you here?

629
00:41:27,471 --> 00:41:29,951
Su Jeong asked me for a favor.

630
00:41:29,951 --> 00:41:32,770
Oh? Ju Yeon also asked me for a favor.

631
00:41:32,770 --> 00:41:34,140
Really?

632
00:41:34,140 --> 00:41:36,150
I thought they weren't close anymore.

633
00:41:36,150 --> 00:41:37,920
Was I wrong?

634
00:41:39,409 --> 00:41:41,039
It's definitely good to see you.

635
00:41:41,039 --> 00:41:42,489
I'm leaving now.

636
00:41:42,489 --> 00:41:44,019
Okay.

637
00:41:44,739 --> 00:41:47,088
- Drive carefully. - Okay.

638
00:41:59,366 --> 00:42:01,876
If she was so happy to see me,

639
00:42:01,876 --> 00:42:04,326
She could have gotten out briefly.

640
00:42:25,552 --> 00:42:28,142
What are you doing? Pack the rest of your things.

641
00:42:28,142 --> 00:42:30,722
Yes, I should do that.

642
00:42:35,361 --> 00:42:37,561
We are in the parking garage.

643
00:42:37,561 --> 00:42:40,120
You are now in front of the building.

644
00:42:41,060 --> 00:42:42,630
Already?

645
00:42:43,290 --> 00:42:45,589
We've taken the important things away, right?

646
00:42:45,589 --> 00:42:47,539
What should we do with the rest?

647
00:42:47,539 --> 00:42:49,189
If we block the door to this room─

648
00:42:49,189 --> 00:42:50,899
She is already suspicious.

649
00:42:50,899 --> 00:42:52,668
She won't simply go back.

650
00:42:52,668 --> 00:42:54,778
What should we do?

651
00:43:17,995 --> 00:43:21,624
I came to see how you live.

652
00:43:21,624 --> 00:43:23,524
I suspect you're about to leave.

653
00:43:23,524 --> 00:43:24,994
Yes.

654
00:43:24,994 --> 00:43:27,533
I would like to invite you next time, if that would be alright.

655
00:43:27,533 --> 00:43:30,783
You do not need to be invited to inspect your apartment.

656
00:43:30,783 --> 00:43:32,223
Why?

657
00:43:32,223 --> 00:43:35,722
Is there a reason why I shouldn't go to your apartment?

658
00:43:39,761 --> 00:43:41,571
No.

659
00:43:41,571 --> 00:43:45,191
Then let's go up together if it's nothing important.

660
00:44:03,528 --> 00:44:05,898
Take me to the study.

661
00:44:05,898 --> 00:44:07,497
Okay.

662
00:44:40,152 --> 00:44:42,752
It looks normal.

663
00:44:43,842 --> 00:44:47,831
I'm curious why you don't let her clean this room.

664
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:56,140
Are you hiding...

665
00:44:56,140 --> 00:44:59,690
Something in here?

666
00:45:00,719 --> 00:45:02,259
Huh!

667
00:45:30,215 --> 00:45:32,145
I'm sorry.

668
00:45:34,814 --> 00:45:36,414
I'd rather go.

669
00:45:36,414 --> 00:45:39,804
You don't want to go and meet her now.

670
00:45:43,513 --> 00:45:45,283
Stay here.

671
00:46:01,290 --> 00:46:04,580
I thought you were going to do something stupid again.

672
00:46:04,580 --> 00:46:07,399
Did you try to hide this?

673
00:46:08,579 --> 00:46:11,339
I know you wouldn't be happy...

674
00:46:12,239 --> 00:46:14,508
If you knew I had the photo.

675
00:46:16,858 --> 00:46:19,058
I don't have the right...

676
00:46:20,807 --> 00:46:23,427
to cry or to be sad.

677
00:46:24,337 --> 00:46:25,637
Yes.

678
00:46:26,157 --> 00:46:28,056
So why did you keep it if you knew that?

679
00:46:28,056 --> 00:46:29,736
I know...

680
00:46:32,696 --> 00:46:34,855
I do not have the right to

681
00:46:35,505 --> 00:46:38,715
But I wanted to keep at least one photo.

682
00:46:43,084 --> 00:46:45,574
Because I miss her so much.

683
00:46:46,374 --> 00:46:49,853
Do you think you have the right to miss her?

684
00:46:57,422 --> 00:46:59,702
If you hadn't been there,

685
00:47:00,492 --> 00:47:03,841
My son would still be here.

686
00:47:06,931 --> 00:47:08,920
Not this stupid photo,

687
00:47:08,920 --> 00:47:11,880
but my real son!

688
00:47:33,707 --> 00:47:35,996
Weak, complete idiot.

689
00:48:01,982 --> 00:48:05,822
From now on, keep a closer eye on him.

690
00:48:05,822 --> 00:48:07,932
Should I have someone monitor him?

691
00:48:08,581 --> 00:48:10,981
I have you, who are watching him.

692
00:48:10,981 --> 00:48:13,281
Who else do we need?

693
00:48:14,081 --> 00:48:17,820
Yes, I will monitor him more closely.

694
00:48:45,356 --> 00:48:47,986
Be careful. You will get hurt.

695
00:48:58,514 --> 00:49:02,023
You know that my parents died in a car accident, right?

696
00:49:05,633 --> 00:49:08,972
We were on our way to an anime event.

697
00:49:08,972 --> 00:49:11,312
They were both busy,

698
00:49:12,542 --> 00:49:16,351
But I begged her to let me leave.

699
00:49:17,441 --> 00:49:20,141
That's when we got into an accident on the way.

700
00:49:21,301 --> 00:49:24,270
Thanks to their protection, I survived.

701
00:49:25,140 --> 00:49:26,780
But they died in the accident.

702
00:49:26,780 --> 00:49:29,139
in which they shouldn't have been because of me.

703
00:49:30,489 --> 00:49:34,559
My grandmother actually lost her only son because of me.

704
00:49:35,588 --> 00:49:38,748
So I decided to make it up to them.

705
00:49:41,188 --> 00:49:44,947
To become the person she wants to be, the one who replaces my father.

706
00:49:47,077 --> 00:49:48,927
Director.

707
00:49:57,595 --> 00:49:59,815
But even after that

708
00:50:00,925 --> 00:50:04,044
I still couldn't give up my joy.

709
00:50:04,044 --> 00:50:06,834
The next volume of my favorite cartoon

710
00:50:06,834 --> 00:50:09,823
and the new song and the bands' show.

711
00:50:11,403 --> 00:50:13,873
I need things like that...

712
00:50:15,443 --> 00:50:18,202
to look forward to tomorrow.

713
00:50:22,631 --> 00:50:27,131
Although nobody loved me, I was content.

714
00:50:31,830 --> 00:50:33,620
And that's why

715
00:50:35,710 --> 00:50:39,619
I was truly happy when you showed me at the fountain

716
00:50:39,619 --> 00:50:43,778
You said that I should like things,

717
00:50:46,968 --> 00:50:49,467
that I like.

718
00:50:51,727 --> 00:50:54,137
That's what I meant too.

719
00:50:55,157 --> 00:50:56,986
You have

720
00:50:58,426 --> 00:51:01,646
She really looked happy back then.

721
00:51:03,345 --> 00:51:07,255
I wanted you to continue being happy.

722
00:51:17,303 --> 00:51:19,163
I like you.

723
00:51:23,003 --> 00:51:26,482
I hid the things I like for a long time.

724
00:51:27,582 --> 00:51:30,281
Because everything I liked was a secret.

725
00:51:30,281 --> 00:51:33,491
That's why I couldn't tell you, but

726
00:51:37,560 --> 00:51:40,730
I really like you a lot, Baek Su Jeong.

727
00:51:46,829 --> 00:51:49,259
I'm sorry I couldn't keep this to myself.

728
00:51:52,078 --> 00:51:54,318
Thank you for what you did today.

729
00:52:37,081 --> 00:52:38,191
There's my daughter.

730
00:52:38,191 --> 00:52:40,391
Yes, Dad. You're home.

731
00:52:40,391 --> 00:52:41,761
What are you talking about?

732
00:52:41,761 --> 00:52:43,501
You had asked me to receive packages.

733
00:52:43,501 --> 00:52:46,070
The people were there, delivered them, and left again.

734
00:52:46,070 --> 00:52:49,000
Ah, yes. That's right.

735
00:52:49,000 --> 00:52:50,230
Are you sick?

736
00:52:50,230 --> 00:52:52,629
You had a date. You look terrible.

737
00:52:52,629 --> 00:52:55,149
No, I am not ill.

738
00:52:55,149 --> 00:52:57,998
I asked her to take the packages up to the attic.

739
00:52:57,998 --> 00:53:00,418
Why was there so much stuff?

740
00:53:01,028 --> 00:53:02,948
Someone I know asked me to store them temporarily.

741
00:53:02,948 --> 00:53:04,447
He will bring her back soon.

742
00:53:04,447 --> 00:53:06,927
We don't use the room anyway.

743
00:53:06,927 --> 00:53:10,337
I don't care if they stay longer, but

744
00:53:10,337 --> 00:53:12,786
You're sure you're okay, right?

745
00:53:12,786 --> 00:53:16,816
Of course. Why shouldn't I be doing well?

746
00:53:19,935 --> 00:53:21,625
Su Jeong.

747
00:53:21,625 --> 00:53:22,895
Hm?

748
00:53:22,895 --> 00:53:24,824
Do you know,

749
00:53:25,524 --> 00:53:28,474
When you smile like that, it breaks my heart.

750
00:53:28,474 --> 00:53:30,544
Because I'm not good enough

751
00:53:30,544 --> 00:53:33,973
And because you can't rely on me...

752
00:53:33,973 --> 00:53:36,813
Because you can't tell me if anything is wrong,

753
00:53:36,813 --> 00:53:39,482
I wonder if that's why you're smiling like that.

754
00:53:39,482 --> 00:53:41,272
Also...

755
00:53:42,492 --> 00:53:44,132
Dad,

756
00:53:44,132 --> 00:53:47,221
Please don't worry, it's nothing.

757
00:53:47,221 --> 00:53:51,100
I'm just tired because I've been traveling for a while.

758
00:53:51,820 --> 00:53:54,400
Okay, then. Go to your room and rest.

759
00:53:55,010 --> 00:53:56,220
Then you go to your room too.

760
00:53:56,220 --> 00:53:57,679
Okay.

761
00:54:14,417 --> 00:54:16,927
You smile a lot.

762
00:54:16,927 --> 00:54:18,976
You don't usually smile.

763
00:54:18,976 --> 00:54:21,676
What can I do to make you feel better?

764
00:54:23,676 --> 00:54:26,855
Isn't it tiring to work alone?

765
00:54:26,855 --> 00:54:28,785
And it's lonely, too.

766
00:54:41,133 --> 00:54:43,903
I hid the things I like for a long time.

767
00:54:43,903 --> 00:54:46,722
Because everything I liked was a secret.

768
00:54:46,722 --> 00:54:49,632
That's why I couldn't tell you, but

769
00:54:50,532 --> 00:54:53,601
I really like you a lot, Baek Su Jeong.

770
00:55:16,688 --> 00:55:25,156
♫

771
00:55:25,156 --> 00:55:31,785
♫

772
00:55:31,785 --> 00:55:38,195
♫

773
00:55:38,195 --> 00:55:40,754
I know that's crazy, but

774
00:55:40,754 --> 00:55:42,724
I can remember everything.

775
00:55:43,814 --> 00:55:45,403
That was

776
00:55:46,873 --> 00:55:48,793
My first kiss.

777
00:55:48,793 --> 00:55:52,732
♫

