♫

788
00:56:30,447 --> 00:56:31,947
Director.

789
00:56:32,766 --> 00:56:34,966
Director, are you in there?

790
00:56:34,966 --> 00:56:37,716
I would like to ask you something.

791
00:56:38,936 --> 00:56:43,035
♫

792
00:56:43,035 --> 00:56:46,694
♫

793
00:56:46,694 --> 00:56:51,534
♫

