♫

799
00:57:35,537 --> 00:57:37,937
So this is where you are.

800
00:57:40,916 --> 00:57:42,756
Baek Su Jeong.

801
00:57:43,556 --> 00:57:46,096
I wanted to know something.

802
00:57:46,705 --> 00:57:48,925
That's why I'm here.

803
00:57:51,275 --> 00:57:55,694
When you remembered that you kissed me,

804
00:57:56,494 --> 00:57:59,444
Why did you flee here then?

805
00:58:00,543 --> 00:58:03,583
You knew it was crazy to do that.

806
00:58:04,383 --> 00:58:07,402
So, if you showed up dressed like that, the things you were hiding,

807
00:58:08,482 --> 00:58:10,952
the secrets you have so carefully kept,

808
00:58:10,952 --> 00:58:14,801
They can be uncovered. You knew that.

809
00:58:14,801 --> 00:58:17,181
So why did you come?

810
00:58:21,230 --> 00:58:24,010
Just because you like me?

811
00:58:24,010 --> 00:58:26,250
For that reason alone?

812
00:58:33,898 --> 00:58:35,988
Would that be okay?

813
00:58:37,358 --> 00:58:40,477
Our relationship could be exposed at any time

814
00:58:40,477 --> 00:58:43,397
And that could be a problem for your dream of becoming Yongsung's successor.

815
00:58:43,397 --> 00:58:45,557
represent.

816
00:58:47,416 --> 00:58:49,116
I

817
00:58:51,486 --> 00:58:54,445
I think that would be okay.

818
00:58:54,445 --> 00:58:57,015
as long as I have you.

819
